DPRM-DLLM contains original reusable DPRM controller code plus lightweight
integration overlays derived from local research forks.

Host projects referenced by the overlays:

- PUMA: https://github.com/JaeyeonKim01/PUMA
- DPLM: https://github.com/bytedance/dplm
- DMPO: https://github.com/yuchen-zhu-zyc/DMPO
- Prism: https://github.com/viiika/Prism

This repository does not redistribute checkpoints, datasets, W&B artifacts, or
complete upstream host repositories. Users should consult each upstream project
for its own license, model terms, dataset terms, and reproduction instructions.

